<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>= 演大片！电影级声光音效 =</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/734a769a4b1d490b9cd14eb74dd1283e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
