<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>= 超还原！牢房、医院...真实复刻！=</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200914/f9b52dd0c4b644489d578439c525dfd3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
